      <div class="msgContentFrame">Ok, I have a physical level 11 rank 9 lancer. I followed forum advice and got both second wind and bloodbath, and that has really helped. Now I'm just trying to figure out what gathering / crafting classes will help me. I am in a pretty good LS that will help me get a harpoon if we can get fish glue, so I thought about fishing with cooking, but that won't help me directly, so I thought about leatherworking for armor. Really, I just want to know what others are doing and think is useful for a lancer. Also how do I know what my xp fatigue is at for each class?  <br /> <br />Thanks for any help, <br />Geldon</div>
