      <div class="msgContentFrame">Unfortunately, square decided to make the crafting system entirely non-obvious. While some spears require carpentry to make, others require goldsmith. And lances, when the recipes are finally found, will probably be blacksmith.  <br />So... sticking with just 1 profession isn't going to cut it if you want to be self-sufficient, even with repairing your own gear.</div>
